Additional details

Safety Information

Keep out of reach of children and pets. Each heat cell contains iron (2 grams): Can be harmful if ingested. If ingested, rinse mouth with warm water and call a Poisonous Control Center immediately. Do not microwave or attempt to reheat as wrap could catch fire. This product can cause burns. 55 or older: Your risk of burning increases as you age. Wear ThermaCare over a layer of clothing, not directly against your skin. Do not wear while sleeping. Check skin frequently during use. Do not wear for more than 8 hours in any 24-hour period.

Indications

menstrual cramping

Ingredients

Iron, Sodium Chloride, Sodium thiosulfate, Water, Charcoal, Sodium Polyacylate

Directions

Place the ThermaCare heatwrap below your belly button with the adhesive side against your undergarments. Adjust the heatwrap and press firmly to the heatwrap into place.
